title: GPACK
message:
[CENTER][COLOR=#808080][B]NOTE: This pack will receive updates with new content (and revised ones that broke in 0.14). It is rather small atm.[/B][/COLOR]
[B]Some stuff is not working properly in 0.10 and the 0.10.1 patch. A quick fix addon will be released. In the mean time 0.10.1 will be tagged as Unsupported.[/B]
[ATTACH]486031[/ATTACH]
[I]New configs for many...[/I]

[ATTACH]486037[/ATTACH][/CENTER]

[B][COLOR=#0080ff]Info:[/COLOR][/B] I mentioned GPACK before, it went through different versions and themes. This car pack features configurations for various cars along with performance parts, new lights, decals, bumpers, RHD converts, wheels and other cosmetic enhancements. Each featured config uses a custom part of some kind. You can make a stunning sleeper for a horrendous rice burner, your call. This version of GPACK is completely lore-friendly, (hopefully) compatible with other mods, no overwriting and will be used as a base for future GPACK extensions ([URL='https://www.beamng.com/threads/apack.58141/']APACK[/URL] is not involved).

[CENTER][ATTACH]486036[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486030[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486035[/ATTACH][/CENTER]

[B][COLOR=#0080ff]Highlights:[/COLOR][/B] This pack adds new configurations to various cars. These configs include new performance parts, various cosmetic parts like lights and bumpers and ways to completely deck out your ride!
[CENTER][SPOILER="Examples"]-Supercharged Hopper and I-Series.
-Overpowered JATO jets for DT40
-New lights and fascias for various cars (most listed as Aftermarket).
-New wheels, both factory branded or custom.
-RHD SBR4, 1999 Pessima and Hopper.
-New interiors and cloth colors for Hopper
-New bumpers for various cars
-Custom interiors for various cars[/SPOILER][/CENTER]

[CENTER][ATTACH]486038[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486039[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486040[/ATTACH][/CENTER]

[B][COLOR=#0080ff]Cars involved (as of 0.10):[/COLOR][/B]
Bruckell LeGran
Civetta Bolide
ETK 800
ETK K-Series
ETK I-Series
Gavril D-Series
Gavril Grand Marshal
Hirochi SBR4
[COLOR=#404040]Hirochi Sunburst
Ibishu 200BX
Ibishu Pessima (Both gens)
Ibishu Covet
Ibishu Hopper
Wentward DT40[/COLOR]

[B][COLOR=#0080ff]Installation:[/COLOR][/B] Click Subscribe or manually download and place in your mods folder!

[B][COLOR=#0080ff]Compatibility:[/COLOR][/B][COLOR=#404040] Requires BeamNG 0.14 (October 30, 2018) or later!
[/COLOR]
[COLOR=#0080ff][B]Notes:[/B][/COLOR] [I][COLOR=rgb(64, 64, 64)][U]Some parts don't have the highest quality. You will have to search for some of the parts.[/U][/COLOR][/I][COLOR=#404040] New parts will be regularly added. Bellco superchargers are using old V8 models and may or may not be updated. Some cars may have easter eggs. :rolleyes:[/COLOR] [COLOR=#bfbfbf]cough d-series[/COLOR]

[CENTER][ATTACH]486041[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486042[/ATTACH][ATTACH]486033[/ATTACH][/CENTER]

[CENTER][I]Some parts were made by Tommy1995, used with permission. Credits to vehicles are for the BeamNG Team. Everything in this mod is lore-friendly.[/I]
